{"tid":673012,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【夏威夷爆火山毒霧摧毀香港樓市】災區俯瞰片如「火地獄」 熔岩流入太平洋產生毒霧","createTime":"2018-05-21T12:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T12:57:28.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6fdd46fe76d7d9b26eb400a170fc0f49faab58","tid":673012,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180521/58218076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58218076&d=06Ej3lOb8dMH8tBioTijC%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8b9aa6a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58218076&h=4d3d2d07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180521/58218076</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷基拉韋厄（Kilauea）火山最新一次爆發所噴出的岩漿，不但令一名男子受傷，而且已越過一條高速公路，流入太平洋，引發另一場危機。<br />\n高空俯瞰片段可見，熔岩流經之處林木均化為灰燼，新一輪岩漿噴發又摧毀4間屋，熔岩並濺傷一名男子小腿。當時他坐在住所三樓露台，被飛來的熔岩擊傷。<br />\n岩漿周日流過一條用於疏散沿岸居民的重要高速公路，進入太平洋。熾熱岩漿遇上海水，產生含鹽酸和玻璃微粒的霧霾（laze），可刺激眼、皮膚、肺，導致呼吸困難。夏威夷火山觀察站表示，這種帶腐蝕性的氣體，曾在2000年導致2人死亡。<br />\n基拉韋厄火山是世界上最活躍火山之一，兩周前開始噴發，已摧毀普納區（Puna）44座民宅與其他<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建築物</span>。"}]}